 2023-03872023-04-28PWGSC
ActNational Capital Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of KENNETH JOSEPH HUGHES of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a member of the Board of Directors of the National Capital Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Deborah Lynn Morrison, whose term has expired.
